| 1  |   NESTED LOOPS OUTER    |       |        | 1    | 2    | 0         |       |        |
| 2  |       TABLE ACCESS FULL | SYS   | SSE_T1 | 1    | 1    | 0         |       |        |
| 3  |       TABLE ACCESS FULL | SYS   | SSE_T2 | 3    | 1    | 0         |       |        |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Predicate Information (identified by id):                       
-----------------------------------------                       
    2 - filter: SSE_T1.B = 2                                    
    3 - filter: SSE_T1.B = 2 AND SSE_T1.A = SSE_T2.A            

